cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.SD, cs.SI, cs.CL 

This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) category as it deals with video analysis algorithms for speaker detection. It may also belong to Multimedia (cs.MM) as it involves audio-visual data. Signal Processing (cs.SD) is another possible category as it deals with audio processing. Additionally, Speech and Natural Language Processing (cs.CL) and Social and Information Networks (cs.SI) could also be relevant categories as the dataset can be used for speech enhancement and human-robot interaction.
